{"tid":1632262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理Sor","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:40:38.000Z","uid":258784,"like":42,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"f7e0ecf01d6cd8733b0a84a26bf359293a95d2a8","tid":1632262,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:00.000Z","msg":"Popo預咗聽日大家繼續大搞，不如試下出其不意，嚟個終極和理非，大家響18區同受影響嘅人 致歉<br />\n<br />\n原因如下：<br />\n1)呢幾日交通食晒屎，真係有人開始屌鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2)俾勇武手足抖下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3)增加同群眾互動，俾人更了解我地嘅理念<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4)出其不意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5)的確有唔少人接受唔到裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請緊記，得民心者得天下，唔好似住有一定嘅民意就諗住做咩都得，我地爭取民主，就係想要一個顧及大多數人感受嘅制度。<br />\n<br />\n我知道應該會好多負皮，但係希望大家做每一件事之前諗一諗幫唔幫到成件事"},{"pid":"96629071f789e1627b17209eadfb7b918693bb8c","tid":1632262,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:14.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c87fcb70c8b7479b0c2fc1cc4983c242d0fb7a33","tid":1632262,"uid":207596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57a5d830ccaa77d927b50a9abd87c4a911587fcd","tid":1632262,"uid":142010,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:21.000Z","msg":"對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修<br />\n<br />\n1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX<br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.MEMO紙<br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.善用1823<br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.蟲系魔法師<br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):<br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚<br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢飛個靚髮或者化下妝就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命<br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"40118da8b3b9105da62d5a634a208d4b2b746b0e","tid":1632262,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:41.000Z","msg":"[公投] 黎緊幾日勇武定和理<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632191\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632191</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"323f1df1946dddd7a513a2bb95ff6b653d09b926","tid":1632262,"uid":39547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:30:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83a696450c94f8f41e6b11f9d3d3886a82742a1b","tid":1632262,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:30:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0be36f3d43b12dabd87791dc0df7e4936e4c6350","tid":1632262,"uid":114951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:26.000Z","msg":"和理sor<br />\n和理宣<br />\n勇武和理非一齊做<br />\n跟住個禮拜全力開火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a3ef6b2e10d33e0a1e3b800271dc092b8537bd","tid":1632262,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75d75003db118c1621451a630f805aee47bc2a40","tid":1632262,"uid":5526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa965cbf15b0df4324979ac94232359000c01358","tid":1632262,"uid":5526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0231a125f07e6745e6215680e1bf944ee40eda63","tid":1632262,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f6a7d0f25c68c1de03543f72fd94a4a60e5ec4a","tid":1632262,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:23.000Z","msg":"聽日18區繼續開花，<br />\n不過係連儂牆開花，<br />\n雷神錘休息。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc5cf845a9cd3e7622ac51a2969d26ea1c6d890","tid":1632262,"uid":9049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:32.000Z","msg":"道歉+譴責警方喬裝示威者"},{"pid":"67ab491abf8bbe9cd610c7d63842a5bfd3f68f6c","tid":1632262,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:45.000Z","msg":"「認真」各位手足 借東風啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7374b8840230a817a17410f5e455e07b9e4e4c46","tid":1632262,"uid":226819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"474689562dbbb4ad15e1ae8e7e03896f1424fb09","tid":1632262,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c997bf94a6ec4e893c632414136be243794acf63","tid":1632262,"uid":246741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:36:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb27f17e50ebb42888dae56ba688b2c9ffaba521","tid":1632262,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:37:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b47afd91ac9db83df54b2f26217930f8e6effae","tid":1632262,"uid":14563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:37:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家手牽手玩得咁成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實可唔可以手牽手和理sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a0be58b8da474438bb420c279769a6661bd159cc","tid":1632262,"uid":8116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:38:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e869b4c697410f7931c3030f0a9e13c5c8040a5","tid":1632262,"uid":141097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fa0514a61c098a3cba2116cc6c35c3fece5faf","tid":1632262,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:43:07.000Z","msg":"我覺得需要黎多次<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">和理sor</span></strong><br />\n除左文宣/增加正當性/外媒目光<br />\n譴責警察喬裝示威者，破壞和平遊行<br />\n<br />\n和理Sor<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632262</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nSignature簽名檔：守護香港，深層改革<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">9月9重陽節活動：祈求先人保佑我們！<br />\n冇人鍾意亂咁裝修嘅師傅！<br />\n國際戰線跟唔上，文宣要人！</span><br />\n<br />\n抗爭轉型及進化建議：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">持久戰拖垮邪惡</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">重要目標：</span></strong>11月24號區議會選舉、香港民主及人權法案、和平勇武後勤文宣議員：各司其職<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">強調：</span></strong>愛港市民、良知、美國制裁、親北京賣港賊、大話精、傀儡、暴政殘害人民、公平公正選舉、為港人服務<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">防範：</span></strong>掌心雷、利誘淺黃淺藍市民、抹黑<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">流水式示威：</span></strong>警察舉旗咪去另一個地方示威，香港咁多地方可以去，佢想捉你，你咪話走緊囉，太多人行得慢好正常，合情合理合法！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">適當武力/自衛反擊：</span></strong>合情又合理！<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>游擊戰？：</strong></span>對抗黑社會/恐怖分子<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">創意活動：抗爭融入生活</span></strong>唱歌比賽？跑步大叫？商場罷買？摺紙？#Shout4HK#諗到再加<br />\n<br />\n公平、自由、民主、公義、人權<span style=\"color: gold;\">得來不易</span><br />\n漫長的道路上需要<span style=\"color: gold;\">你支持我，我扶持你</span><br />\n有時惘然若失，但我們也要<span style=\"color: gold;\">自信往前邁步</span><br />\n有咩嘢唔想失去，就努力<span style=\"color: gold;\">捍衛</span>同<span style=\"color: gold;\">守護</span><br />\n現在就用自己雙手實踐夢想，<span style=\"color: gold;\">迎接未來</span><br />\n<br />\n短期目標：改善抗爭能力，提升身份認同<br />\n建議：文宣！各有各做，best effort <br />\n中期目標：區議會(94%民主產生)<br />\n建議：關注身邊人，團結一致，各有各做<br />\n長期目標：強化黃色陣營、民主/黃色經濟圈<br />\n建議：抗爭生活化，減少比錢極權陣營<br />\n終極目標：民選議會、民選政府<br />\n建議：國際戰線、傳播思想、滲透內部<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公務員</span></strong>：小隱於野，中隱於市，大隱於朝<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和勇合一</strong></span>：1.合法之下，最大勇武<br />\n                     2. 做任何事，永不被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">@謠言係疫症&bull;不傳播&bull;去求診&bull;澄清藥<br />\n@FakeNews係Cancer&bull;不擴散&bull;求事實&bull;割<br />\n@接觸資訊時，腦袋要清醒</span><br />\n<br />\n只要爭取民主團火未熄，還是有機會達成<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">衛城革命，生活抗爭</span><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\n<strong><em>升級技能/能力值</em></strong>：1. 讀書、識法律2.運動、鬥長命3.和勇合一精神4.批判性思考5.精通專業技能<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMdiioB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMdiioB.jpg&h=7e10cb33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpg5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=ff9c3b50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n理非可以做的事<a href=\"https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTakeActionWithYou&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpg5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=a9f1e34a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou</a><br />\n良心與無良商戶<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2F&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpg5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=87c392ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/</a><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\nVersion 2019.10.07<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">要記住極權如何打壓香港示威：</span></strong><br />\n1.抹黑：利用少部分的暴力衝突而將全部示威者形容為「邪惡」、示威=港獨、新華社、環球時報、人民日報<br />\n2.誤導：警總救護車、雷射槍、9吋尖刀等等<br />\n3.滲透：5毛、陳雲、黃x民、譚香文<br />\n4.假民意/曲解民意：主流民意是......<br />\n5.5毛輿論-分化、負面、fake news、煽動手足做負效益/低效益工作<br />\n6.強迫企業自我審查<br />\n7.出動黑社會、愛國暴徒<br />\n8.扮示威者：(負面的)破壞eg.遊行<br />\n9.嫁禍示威者/黑警：打議員打記者打女仔<br />\n10.扮好人/扮對話：「江山易改本性難移」<br />\n11.警察濫權、濫捕、暴力執法、恐嚇<br />\n12.利用親中人士發表「假」權威言論<br />\n13.用盡手段打壓反對聲音<br />\n14.矮化示威者為甲由、yellow object<br />\n15.緊急法：獨裁特首<br />\n諗到再加</span><br />\nSir, my concern is not whether God is on our side; my greatest concern is to be on God's side, for God is always right."},{"pid":"4989b0f6fcefbf50b5752e0dce87a49c59dbf7df","tid":1632262,"uid":86940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:44:12.000Z","msg":"人鏈+sor<br />\n文宣可以出道歉文<br />\n聽日蒙面合唱+重修連儂牆,各位輕裝?冇裝上陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />和和平平都咁比狗驅趕會極引起關注<br />\n 大家加油,今個星期係和理非週<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家好好休息<br />\n休息係為左走更遠既路,晚晚同狗打交唔係目標"},{"pid":"133c7f2f470561c57e2e452e81894ba7a0b9b06e","tid":1632262,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4989b0f6fcefbf50b5752e0dce87a49c59dbf7df","tid":1632262,"uid":86940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:44:12.000Z","msg":"人鏈+sor<br />\n文